<plot>Quietly, an emotional and unyielding drama set in Brooklyn, follows Italis Rivington, a quiet and unassuming 15-year-old, as he struggles to reclaim the blissful years of his childhood. A time long before his mother, Gloria, became irreversibly dependent on her abusive boyfriend, IO. With virtually no options left, Italis is considering drastic action to save his home and his family.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?452154</url></doc>
